title: First family doctor clinic set up at Renji Hospital (Shanghai Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Shanghai Municipal Government ) China's first family doctor clinic that incorporates service method similar to North America opened at the Renji Hospital over the weekend. It will not only serve as a clinic but also as a training
